query:
INSERT INTO agent_votes (sessionId, agentId, agentType, agentProvider, vote, confidence, reasoning) SELECT 1, 'agent_' || n, 
  CASE WHEN n <= 11 THEN 'guardian' WHEN n <= 22 THEN 'arbiter' ELSE 'scribe' END,
  CASE (n-1) % 5 WHEN 0 THEN 'openai' WHEN 1 THEN 'anthropic' WHEN 2 THEN 'google' WHEN 3 THEN 'kimi' ELSE 'deepseek' END,
  CASE WHEN n <= 25 THEN 'approve' WHEN n <= 30 THEN 'reject' ELSE 'escalate' END,
  CAST((0.75 + RANDOM() * 0.25) AS VARCHAR),
  'Evidence clearly demonstrates non-compliance with stated framework requirements.'
FROM generate_series(1, 33) AS n;
